{"tid":2232064,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"藏丫叉鋼珠案 差人被指作口供","createTime":"2020-10-06T06:31:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T06:31:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0f4b4febb921d571c68728276a7dcf11dd5eb0a6","tid":2232064,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T06:31:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201006/K7GKUR2LHJF5LMVAC2HK3TWMJE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201006%2FK7GKUR2LHJF5LMVAC2HK3TWMJE%2F&d=zpUJ%2F0Jv8gnTBnB6SvMaKItKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=85f4fe59\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201006%2FK7GKUR2LHJF5LMVAC2HK3TWMJE%2F&h=00ef5ad4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201006/K7GKUR2LHJF5LMVAC2HK3TWMJE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n藏丫叉鋼珠案 差人被指作口供<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JPJHR5AqFW_ZU4wFEroAekqlTeI=/720x462/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TINFQB5W35CBDFKZTS5GEBGTCI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJPJHR5AqFW_ZU4wFEroAekqlTeI%3D%2F720x462%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTINFQB5W35CBDFKZTS5GEBGTCI.jpg&h=23b0ea3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員陳建鴻<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】今月2月，武漢肺炎指定診所選址惹爭議，天水圍有市民堵路縱火。兩天後，警方在區內截獲兩名男學生，指他們將載有鐵丫叉及89粒鋼珠的紙袋放在行人隧道，兩人否認在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪受審。警員指兩被告在隧道口放下紙袋後交談了數分鐘，他一直在附近駐足觀察。辯方質疑，警員在書面供詞及記事簿中完全沒提過兩人曾停下交談，質疑他作口供；又指閉路電視片段顯示被告手持直身長方形紙袋，但警方撿獲的卻是打橫長方形。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n撿獲紙袋與片段不符<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。前截查兩人。陳同意從沒在供詞及記事簿提及兩被告交談及他曾觀察，但他否認作口供。<br />\n<br />\n控方播放魏的住所大堂閉路電視片段，顯示兩被告一同離開大廈時，各拿兩個袋。陳供稱，兩人各手持的其中一個紙袋，與涉案兩個紙袋一樣。辯方質疑，片中白色袋是直身長方形，撿獲的紙袋則是打橫長方形；陳同意，但謂「我相信係同一個袋」。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：TMCC201/20"}]}